00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:42.420
in our minds, and in our
bodies, and in our psychologies

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:45.740
for the decades, centuries and
thousands of years to come.

00:00:45.740 --> 00:00:49.030
Indeed today, I want to
focus on core mechanisms

00:00:49.030 --> 00:00:52.330
that lead individuals to
seek out other individuals

00:00:52.330 --> 00:00:54.620
with whom to mate with,

00:00:54.620 --> 00:00:57.140
with whom to have children with or not,

00:00:57.140 --> 00:00:58.650
with whom to enter short

00:00:58.650 --> 00:01:00.670
or long-term relationships with,

00:01:00.670 --> 00:01:03.220
