02:20:48.690 --> 02:20:52.620
But in studies that include
both men and women of durations

02:20:52.620 --> 02:20:54.410
anywhere from eight to 12 weeks

02:20:55.350 --> 02:20:57.530
of athletes and non-athletes,

02:20:57.530 --> 02:21:00.590
and different variations of Maca,

02:21:00.590 --> 02:21:03.640
turns out there's black
