02:21:24.659 --> 02:21:27.810
or with the measures that were
performed in these studies.

02:21:27.810 --> 02:21:31.910
But that Maca, again,
consumed in doses of anywhere

02:21:31.910 --> 02:21:34.270
from two to three grams per day,

02:21:34.270 --> 02:21:37.550
has been shown to
significantly increase libido.

02:21:37.550 --> 02:21:42.550
And in fact, those dosages of
